data.title: Maria Feodorovna, Empress of Russia with her four eldest children
data.meta_description: Photograph of Maria Feodorovna, Empress of Russia (1847-1928) with her children Tsesarevich Nicholas (1868-1918), later Nicholas II, Grand Duke George Alexandrovich (1871-99), Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna (1875-1960) and Grand Duke Michael Alexandrovich (1878-1918). Maria Feodorovna and Tsesarevich Nicholas are sitting on a sofa, with Maria Feodorovna to the right with Grand Duke Michael sitting on her knee.
